OL,3,CEight arrests at anti-immigration and
OL,4,Ccounter protest
OL,6,FEight people have been arrested during
OL,7,Fan anti-immigration protest and
OL,8,Fcounter demonstration in Brighton.
OL,10,FSussex Police said an estimated 300
OL,11,Fpeople took part in a Stop The Boats
OL,12,Fprotest on Saturday, while a counter
OL,13,Fprotest organised by Carnival Against
OL,14,FFascism saw around 4,000 attendees.
OL,16,FArrests were made for offences
OL,17,Fincluding assaulting a police officer,
OL,18,Fbreach of the peace, possession of a
OL,19,Fpyrotechnic item and breaching a
OL,20,Fpublic order offence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
