OL,3,CEight arrests at anti-immigration and
OL,4,Ccounter protest
OL,6,FThe anti-immigration march was
OL,7,Forganised by South East Patriots and
OL,8,Fcalled on the government to deport
OL,9,Fillegal immigrants and strengthen
OL,10,Fborder controls.
OL,12,FBefore the protests, Brighton & Hove
OL,13,FCity leader Bella Sankey appealed for
OL,14,Fcalm and said "far right agitators"
OL,15,Fhad no place in the city.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
