PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781439073
OL,3,CEight arrests at anti-immigration and
OL,4,Ccounter protest
OL,6,FSpeaking on a Facebook post she said:
OL,7,F"Brighton and Hove is a proudly
OL,8,Fdiverse city, where white residents,
OL,9,Fblack residents, Muslims, Jews,
OL,10,FChristians, Hindus, Sikhs, people of
OL,11,Fno faith, gay residents, trans
OL,12,Fresidents, feminists, refugees and
OL,13,Fmixed race people like me, live side
OL,14,Fby side peacefully.
OL,16,F"We know better than to blame whole
OL,17,Fcommunities for the actions of
OL,18,Findividuals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
