PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781439073
OL,3,CEight arrests at anti-immigration and
OL,4,Ccounter protest
OL,6,F"This is our home, and in Brighton and
OL,7,FHove, difference is famously our
OL,8,Fstrength."
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Adam Hays,
OL,11,FBrighton and Hove divisional commander
OL,12,Fsaid: "We understand that there was
OL,13,Fsome disruption near the railway
OL,14,Fstation and surrounding roads.
OL,16,F"Public order policing is complex, and
OL,17,Fwhile we understand this can be
OL,18,Ffrustrating, we always balance the
OL,19,Frights of all protest groups and the
OL,20,Fwider community.
OL,26,@tD@GOUxD@AOU
