OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1781439073
OL,3,CEight arrests at anti-immigration and
OL,4,Ccounter protest
OL,6,F"Public safety is always our priority.
OL,7,FI'd like to thank the public for their
OL,8,Fpatience while we worked hard in
OL,9,Fensuring that all of those attending
OL,10,Fthe city, for whatever reason, were
OL,11,Fable to do so safely."
